Package uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.store

Class StoreProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.store.StoreProperties
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AccumuloProperties, FederatedStoreProperties, MapStoreProperties, ProxyProperties
    public class StoreProperties
extends Object
implements Cloneable
    A StoreProperties contains specific configuration information for the store, such as database connection strings. It wraps Properties and lazy loads the all properties from a file when first used.

    All StoreProperties classes must be JSON serialisable.
